    {
      "text": "%python\n\r\n# \u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\r\n# PARAGRAPH 3 — Numba JIT Functions + Warmup\r\n# (Run once per session — warmup triggers compilation)\r\n# \u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\u003d\r\n%python\r\n@jit(nopython\u003dTrue)\r\ndef calculate_dcir_numba(voltage_arr, current_arr, jump_mask):\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate DCIR with Numba JIT acceleration.\"\"\"\r\n    n    \u003d len(voltage_arr)\r\n    dcir \u003d np.full(n, np.nan)\r\n    for i in range(2, n):\r\n        if jump_mask[i]:\r\n            dV \u003d voltage_arr[i] - voltage_arr[i - 2]\r\n            dI \u003d current_arr[i] - current_arr[i - 2]\r\n            if abs(dI) \u003e 10:\r\n                dcir[i] \u003d abs(dV / dI)\r\n    return dcir\r\n\r\n\r\n@jit(nopython\u003dTrue)\r\ndef calculate_dT_dAh_numba(stability_reset, max_temp_arr, current_sum_arr):\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate dT/dAh with Numba JIT acceleration.\"\"\"\r\n    n                 \u003d len(stability_reset)\r\n    Ah_since_stable   \u003d np.zeros(n)\r\n    temp_since_stable \u003d np.zeros(n)\r\n    stable_temp       \u003d np.nan\r\n    cumulative_Ah     \u003d 0.0\r\n    for i in range(n):\r\n        if stability_reset[i]:\r\n            stable_temp   \u003d max_temp_arr[i]\r\n            cumulative_Ah \u003d 0.0\r\n        elif not np.isnan(stable_temp):\r\n            cumulative_Ah        +\u003d current_sum_arr[i] / 60.0\r\n            Ah_since_stable[i]    \u003d cumulative_Ah\r\n            temp_since_stable[i]  \u003d max_temp_arr[i] - stable_temp\r\n    return Ah_since_stable, temp_since_stable\r\n\r\n\r\n# Warmup — triggers JIT compilation now so first real call is instant\r\n_dv \u003d np.array([1.0, 2.0, 3.0])\r\n_jm \u003d np.array([False, False, True])\r\n_ \u003d calculate_dcir_numba(_dv, _dv, _jm)\r\n_ \u003d calculate_dT_dAh_numba(_jm, _dv, _dv)\r\n\r\nprint(\"✅ P3 done — Numba JIT compiled \u0026 warmed up\")\r\n\r\n",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "dateUpdated": "2026-04-13 04:02:31.622",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
        "editorMode": "ace/mode/python",
        "editorHide": false
      },
